==製作過程==
{{tsl|en|Alan Yang|}} 在2009年開始撰寫本電影的劇本。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118006585|title=Alan Yang: 10 Screenwriters to Watch|last=Corcoran|first=Monica|work=Variety|publisher=Reed Buinsess Information|date=July 28, 2009|accessdate=September 30, 2011|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/626D0kpra?url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118006585|archivedate=2011-10-01|deadurl=no}}</ref> 原本本劇是以「同志好友」(Gay Dude)為名，並且是[[狮门娱乐|獅子門]]的十部「微預算」作品之一，總製作費用低於200萬美金。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vancouversun.com/business/technology/Lions+Gate+Entertainment+gives+Vancouver+share+budget+success+story/4530200/story.html|title=Lions Gate Entertainment gives Vancouver a share of its low-budget success story|work=[[The_Vancouver_Sun|The Vancouver Sun]]|date=March 30, 2011|accessdate=September 30, 2011|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/626A6DclO?url=http://lions/#ixzz1ZUUiBY5j|archivedate=2011-10-01|deadurl=no}}</ref>於2011年8月間在[[加拿大|加拿大]][[溫哥華|溫哥華]]境內拍攝。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/archives/ron_tammy_from_parks_recreation_join_gay_dude/|title=Ron & Tammy From 'Parks And Recreation' Join 'Gay Dude'|last=Jagernauth|first=Kevin|publisher=Indiewire. SnagFilms|date=August 12, 2011|accessdate=September 30, 2011|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/626CPcZJ4?url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/archives/ron_tammy_from_parks_recreation_join_gay_dude/|archivedate=2011-10-01|deadurl=yes}}</ref> 

